value.0: This target looks like it's seen better days. It's covered in marks that could only have been made by throwing axes.

There are deep cracks around this embedded hammer, as if it was thrown with great force. Luckily for the dartboard next to it, it seems the thrower had poor aim. Now the hammer won't budge and one must wonder just what the dwarf who threw it must have had to drink that day.
